SuperTurbo Technologies Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 29, 2017 12:06 AM ET
Auto Components

Company Overview of SuperTurbo Technologies Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
SuperTurbo Technologies Inc. specializes in the design, development, and commercialization of SuperTurbos for the global automotive and truck markets. Its SuperTurbo system enables engines and vehicles to achieve important emission reduction, realize fuel savings, and increase overall performance. SuperTurbo Technologies Inc. was formerly known as VanDyne SuperTurbo, Inc. and changed its name to SuperTurbo Technologies Inc. in March 2017. The company was founded in 2009 and is based in Loveland, Colorado.


